        public String[] getLibraryPatterns(String[] libnames,
                                   LibraryTypeEnum libType)
        Description copied from interface: Linker
        Returns a set of filename patterns corresponding to library names. For example, "advapi32" would be expanded to "advapi32.dll" by MsvcLinker and to "libadvapi32.a" and "libadvapi32.so" by GccLinker.
        Parameters:
        libnames - array of library names
